- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper deals with assessing the risk of insider threats and the optimal number of rules to prevent them. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper discusses the coordination of activities among individuals. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is another possible category as the paper touches upon the societal implications of rules and regulations. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses simulations and modeling. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the creation of a Toy Model to examine a work environment.
